title: Set Content Hash for thebadcc.eth to 16 Rand Extension.
body:
This proposal will set the content URL for the ENS domain thebadcc.eth to 16 Rand Extension on Cryptovoxels. 
URL: https://www.cryptovoxels.com/play?coords=W@60E,458S,1.5U
IPFS: QmZPwdVTUmkPQq8DZCE95BaNbKqXn76Tnym45dE8t2w399

Note, 16 Rand Extension is not owned or operated by either the DAO or THEBADCC, LLC. The DAO may amend the content URL for thebadcc.eth at any time under a Proposal.

The Permitted Transaction is as follows:
Address: 0x4976fb03C32e5B8cfe2b6cCB31c09Ba78EBaBa41
Function: setContenthash
Node: 
0x29ca7bc86f86cd48c8c9c53038a6411ab5bd81686dfb0c81dbfa31b738a57222
Hash: 0xe30101701220a4486e3c2c8cbde35725f60fa2e1733a499260986bcad98edafb716d2c9ae8c0
author: 0x4628C15CbD6d11c762E9f95cFc950caa91892D89
